dct_description_sm: Carte dressée par František Machát ; Imprimée par V. Neubert, Prague-Smichov.
Shows waterways, cities, routes (in red), boundaries and disputed territory.
Presence of "Těsín" fully within Czechoslovakian borders suggests date before 1920, when it was divided with Poland.
